    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Wrt54g V5添加usb]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.lofyer.org/blog/2012/10/12/wrt54gs-64ram-8flash/"/>
    <updated>2012-10-12T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.lofyer.org/blog/2012/10/12/wrt54gs-64ram-8flash</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.dd-wrt.com下载固件包及源码包</p>

<p>2.编译添加或者配置usb存储支持</p>

<p>3.按接口图添加usb</p>

<p><a href="http://www.home-wifi.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&page=1&tid=3962" target="_blank"><a href="http://www.home-wifi.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;page=1&amp;tid=3962">http://www.home-wifi.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;page=1&amp;tid=3962</a></a></p>

<blockquote><p>注意焊点位置，两个数据线左边D+，右边D-，下边的472是4.7k的下拉电阻，右边两个电阻是另一组USB口。所以直接引线就可以，但是我的优盘经常不能识别，就又在USB座上把两条数据线对地接了10k的下拉电阻，相当于和图上的472并起来，现在使用很正常。<br/>
<a href="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/bh.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1461" title="bh" src="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/bh.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="367" /></a></p>

<p>使用5V 3A电源给路由器供电，不用安装7805了，电源线直接接到电源插座</p>

<p><a href="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/lbh.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1462" title="lbh" src="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/lbh.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="367" /></a></p>

<p><a href="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dd.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1463" title="dd" src="http://69.164.197.168/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/dd.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="303" /></a></p></blockquote>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content>
